{
  "stem": "11179.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You had your own privacy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the bathrooms were-- they had even water closets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They had cesspools, but nevertheless there were toilet-- regular toilets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they had some electric heather there, there was some heating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That first winter was very cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It snowed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It normally doesn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so we had a kitchen community with electric stoves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But after a year, we couldn't afford it anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we moved to a cheaper place, which didn't have all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But we had actually a little nicer room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But you had a Chinese toilet for yourself, which was just a bucket they picked up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we lived there till-- till-- sometime-- sometime early or in the middle of 1942, when we couldn't afford that anymore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Then we got into a camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But that was difficult to get into a camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We needed-- we needed somebody's help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They were some wealthy Jews in Shanghai who gave a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we found out through a distant cousin of my mother, he told us about that man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He said, he gives a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He had a lot of influence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "If you go to him, you will be able to get from-- they called it kitchen fund at that time, at least a meal a day or two meals a day at a time.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And they would get you in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "My father saw that man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "His name was Newman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He was a manager of a company called [NON-ENGLISH], who was a Swiss-- they were-- they did-- they made cloth, wool, I think, material and something like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was a big company.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And my father thought, the man was very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he helped us to get into the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
